Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.62,0:00:17.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}静心倾听的话 虽然看不见又遥远 但会听到有把声音在歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:24.67,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}在这街道上 看不到能发出那声音的机器 看不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:37.65,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}因为那声音在到达这里前就已被抹掉了听不到那通透的歌声了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:53.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}我听到啊 那小小的声音在你旁边 眼和鼻的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:01:00.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}已经溢满出来了 那绿意的声音如果没人来阻碍的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:12.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}你也是声音的一部份诞生在这广阔的大地上回去吧回到那声音里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:18.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}好怀念 把地震填上节奏的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:22.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}你会看到一个在跳舞的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:25.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}又大又蓝 高高地奏响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:28.89,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}地球交响乐团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你那辫子是我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，今天不做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别说不知道，中国三千年前的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,龙须，藏在什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道是你拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了也不告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,龙须是禁忌的祸根
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,说出来的话，又会有很多人 被卷入争斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,即使要了我这条命也绝不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你意思是不能说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那么去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,四千年前，统治这里的宰相刘白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,及辅助他而名动天下的将军•张贤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在年轻时失去方向而想厌世之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到了云水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,从他身上张贤知道了 千年出现一次的青龙传说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在进入深山等候了十多年后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,张贤终于拿到了龙须
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把它献给了大君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,后来因为龙须而发生了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,龙须的去向也被深埋在历史中了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,近年我幸运地发现 它被当做了小孩的裤带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是最近，又被日出之国的人 带回自己国家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是拿走龙须的人的画像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何都要从这人手中，夺回龙须
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,出发去日本！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,连续剪发狂人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,最近在这市镇，连续发生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻女孩的头发 被剪的不可思议猎奇事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们区内会认为定要尽快找出对策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因此，无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,需要天下无双兼且日本第一高手的 天道先生负责市内巡视和警备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,天下无双，兼且日本第一高手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,千万拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,专门剪辫子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,被害人好像全是留辫子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟为了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说我是最好的饵诱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你那辫子，是我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等你们好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,终于出来了，剪发狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛，意外地又小又弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好像在商量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好像已经谈好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们逃了，乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,逃得真快的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，你让他们逃掉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你那辫子，是我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你们啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,同样的手法竟然连用两次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这次绝不会让你们逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来，给我看看你们的脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,肉包子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,什么！ 我们哪里像肉包子啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那你像什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么看也是肉包子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,难道，这些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会是豆沙包？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是肉包子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是豆沙包！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,肉包子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,（咖喱包） 豆沙包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,住口，住口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,天津甘栗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,南京鸡蛋薄烧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们当人家是什么？ （可能是薄饼包子呢）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有熊猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,住口，住口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,肉包子也好豆沙包也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这并不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,应该还有更重要的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，你们为什么要剪走辫子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不能说，即使你要了我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在找龙须
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,龙须？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,（龙须是什么？ ）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是龙…龙须
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里像啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不用说了 你那条辫子是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,剪发狂人，完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,（也可能是沙律包子呢）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,听到龙须的时候，乱马好不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,龙须究竟是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,现在怎能被拿走？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,比想象中更强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这里必须用计谋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,迫不得已时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在四千年前，统治本地的是 宰相刘白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,辅助他而名动天下的将军•张贤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在年轻时失去方向而想厌世之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到了云水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,从他身上张贤知道了在云海深处 千年出现一次的青龙传说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在进入深山，等候了十多年后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,张贤千辛万苦，终于拿到了龙须
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是晨操而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔，乱马，吃早饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在激动什么，乱马？冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,龙须究竟是什么，乱马？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是装修工人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你上油漆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,全被挡开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这下糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,满头都是油漆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没恶意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快去洗洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快去，快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不用你们说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会去洗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要洗干净啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧•乱马？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,走廊都是油漆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜，拿毛巾来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶，那些肉包子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，解开辫子吧，这样子不好洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不松开洗的话，油漆会洗不干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马真懒惰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，大家在替你担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你解开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的头发！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么也不肯的话，只好硬来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让你逃了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那么讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这事不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来人，快拦住他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,（给我安静！ ）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真会麻烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小靡，好好抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,的确没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,绑这辫子的带子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是中国四千年的秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,龙须！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,龙须…是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事，乱马？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，龙须究竟是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这龙须，是我的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,封印？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,封印？ （充公）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,封印
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,封印
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果解开了辫子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,会发生可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶，洗个头害我都没时间吃早饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，你在生什么气？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你那辫子的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了，这种事没什么好说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不好，因为你正被追击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那些肉包子，我不会这么算数的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然已经找到龙须
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙比想象中更麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不一定要用武力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么好办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧，过去交给我的事中 有失败过的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么说我真难开口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你已经两次袭击都失败了啰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得那的确是你的计划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，我已经不想再飞天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别怪我这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你们说话意外地坦白嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那是加了安眠药的肉包子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,经过的人会拿来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,趁他睡着时，我们把他的辫子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一刀剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,完美的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不只我们两人迟到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,迟到就是迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,发生意想不到的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,被其他人先捡起来吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真是些嘴馋的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,又失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:17:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可能应该用更积极的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是第三次失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,等他一个人时袭击他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马那家伙，结果最重要的事 还是没告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,解开辫子的话，就会发生可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶，肚子好饿没力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很想吃肉包子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那就给你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们害得你没早饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,力量应该只剩下了一半
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就等着你一个人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧，肉包子攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,放了麻醉气体的麻气包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,已经无法动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你那辫子，我们收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,糟…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马真是的，上课中究竟跑哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶，身体不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到龙须了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,终于拿到龙须啰！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是龙须？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是条绳子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,振作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,难得你这次计谋很成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜，如果你武功再高一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊，的确太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又被打飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经是第四次了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这次比较痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，你在里面吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要进来了，乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是乱马吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，在的话回答我一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你…真的是乱马吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，你究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马竟然有这样的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可是当男人真辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.79,0:23:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,当男人的野心完尽时…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,敬请期待啊
